  "body": "# Problem\r\n\r\nWhen last message contains text that end in new line the following(see screenshot) happens\r\n- the chat in the list has height greater than it is supposed to be\r\n\r\n![Simulator Screen Shot - iPhone Xs - 2019-09-12 at 18 04 15](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42058840/64783861-867b3200-d588-11e9-9206-917798683f17.png)\r\n\r\nSeems to be a known but ignored bug in react-native itself\r\nhttps://github.com/facebook/react-native/issues/21612\r\n\r\nTo reproduce the bug\r\n- go to any chat\r\n- type something that ought to fit in one line but ends with new-line, send it\r\n- go back to chat-list/home",
